{
  "text": "Wolf et al. recently reported that long-term feeding an HFCD diet to mice can induce HCC, which depends on intrahepatic CD8+ T cells and NKT cells [CITATION_1] . In our microarray analysis results, many genes known to affect the immune response exceeded the twofold cutoff.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "10903698"
